Society of Industrial Engineering or SIE is an academic organization based in University of Perpetual Help System DALTA - Calamba Campus exclusive for BS Industrial Engineering students, faculty and alumni of the said university. It is one of the seven student organizations under the College of Engineering and Architecture of the university which includes MES (Mechanical Engineering Society) for BS Mechanical Engineering students and ACES (Association of Civil Engineering Students) for BS Civil Engineering among others. The society is also a member of PIIE (Philippine Institute of Industrial Engineers), a premier organization of BS Industrial Engineering graduates and students, and IE professionals in the Philippines. Engr. Ester Velarde is the society's adviser aside from being an IE coordinator in the university.
